  <brief_title>Vertebral Augmentation and Radiotherapy of Collapse Spinal Metastatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Vertebral Augmentation and Radiotherapy in Painful or at Risk of Collapse Spinal Metastatic Cancer/Multiple Myeloma</official_title>
